message: Grunt build system + bower scaffolding (for builds with and without dependencies pre-bundled).

Fixed compilation problems introduced by Bootstrap (now requires less >1.4). 
Mentioned in #282.
Added testem and grunt-cli to package.json deps.
Use karma for all test running.
Coverage reporting + restored original browser matrix + other fixes.
Added ability to control browsers from command line when testing locally.
Bump sifter dependency to fix installing on Node v6 - brianreavis/sifter.js#40
define npm standard commands within package.json

Add mocha and chai as devDependencies

Npm 3+ doesn't install them automatically.
widen jQuery dep to v2 and v3

Merge pull request #1414 from graingert/patch-1

move jquery to peerDependencies
add syntax highlighting and documentation updates
correct version variable, homepage in package.json
node-sass & grunt-sass instead of grunt-contrib-sass w/ ruby
move sifter.js to /contrib to avoid vuln warning in sifter/bin
smaller bundle, update microplugin, sifter, babel.conf
build custom.js and build each plugin.js individually
